### List User
GET http://localhost:8001/user/list?offset=0&limit=20

### Get User
GET http://localhost:8001/user/1

### Create User
POST http://localhost:8001/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria.silva@example.com",
  "password_hash": "hashed_password_123",
  "phone": "+55 11 99999-9999",
  "role": "member",
  "active": true
}

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:8001/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria S. Oliveira",
  "email": "maria.oliveira@example.com",
  "password_hash": "new_hashed_password",
  "phone": "+55 11 98888-8888",
  "role": "librarian",
  "active": true
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:8001/user/1
